{"tid":1036904,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀唔讀pure sci 既Mphil好","createTime":"2019-02-25T14:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T06:46:35.000Z","uid":92717,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad7a87edd53b97902a2772b7d38e423871745c0","tid":1036904,"uid":92717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:12:46.000Z","msg":"今年final year 仲未諗好要讀research 定做野好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日有個professor 問我有冇興趣去佢group 讀mphil ，佢係做physical chemistry 既。<br />\n(之前有問過佢話都話冇錢唔收學生，而家話可以收個mphil)<br />\n有冇巴打讀過呢個field 既research 可以share 吓<br />\n預咗呢個field 除咗讀上之外對搵工零幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ff67c4205489d64f22c6f7820b05dfdcb0aa2a","tid":1036904,"uid":183035,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:25:58.000Z","msg":"之後喺院校撈返一官半職做下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f241d96af30dad674a7d7c77101c3aa180b3aa","tid":1036904,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"機會難得"},{"pid":"c1a338eaa4adc1a2b3f06957689d462271190006","tid":1036904,"uid":37489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711340a3915f1aa952330b7d93a30a65c29350a4","tid":1036904,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T00:36:46.000Z","msg":"唔等錢駛又有興趣咪試吓囉<br />\n但對事業發展零幫助，少兩年工作經驗，你自己諗。"},{"pid":"f012d733f646ecf8247e48046c006384b95be69d","tid":1036904,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T00:59:35.000Z","msg":"phy chem好𨶙難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係止識chem<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a19ffc2458195b29e8edd7eea69ece57c2753e1","tid":1036904,"uid":52342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"香港唔好<br />\n英美可考慮<br />\n但chem係夕陽科目黎<br />\n確保skills transferrable<br />\nEg coding skills for computational phy chem"},{"pid":"65d44ca9751f32d5e319f77586f6455bc8e43f9a","tid":1036904,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:06:34.000Z","msg":"Phy chem好少人讀係幾難得<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，出路都窄，本地無乜Phy chem topic，要做就要出歐美或者教書。你睇你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMphil玩得過PhD就玩唔過"},{"pid":"157f83dc78cbb65fc680c199e59b3b45a8549abf","tid":1036904,"uid":52342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:08:31.000Z","msg":"佢仲話無錢收學生<br />\n如果係香港 即代表兩樣野<br />\n佢係ap or rap funding 少兼朝不保夕 6年內無成績比人炒<br />\n佢唔識r關係叫full prof代收學生<br />\n咁你畢左業都無人脈 佢都幫唔到你搵工 到時自求多福"},{"pid":"5c48ed4f32a4013dcda47b170af2fe81c79aaaf6","tid":1036904,"uid":100871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />`"},{"pid":"ac855f2dbac50292037495885f7a6afdb454de54","tid":1036904,"uid":92717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a19ffc2458195b29e8edd7eea69ece57c2753e1","tid":1036904,"uid":52342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"香港唔好<br />\n英美可考慮<br />\n但chem係夕陽科目黎<br />\n確保skills transferrable<br />\nEg coding skills for computational phy chem"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"我身都唔識打code <br />\n問過佢group 既學生話佢都係入左去讀之後先學識programming 既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得可以當個機會學多d 數同programming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c848fa81eb4d77550f9d0eee5770bac7ede1d20","tid":1036904,"uid":92717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1a338eaa4adc1a2b3f06957689d462271190006","tid":1036904,"uid":37489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"唔係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> s字頭嘅"},{"pid":"5dc39c15a57b6d3889492207a33687d867b02354","tid":1036904,"uid":52342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac855f2dbac50292037495885f7a6afdb454de54","tid":1036904,"uid":92717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a19ffc2458195b29e8edd7eea69ece57c2753e1","tid":1036904,"uid":52342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:04:47.000Z","msg":"香港唔好<br />\n英美可考慮<br />\n但chem係夕陽科目黎<br />\n確保skills transferrable<br />\nEg coding skills for computational phy chem"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"我身都唔識打code <br />\n問過佢group 既學生話佢都係入左去讀之後先學識programming 既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得可以當個機會學多d 數同programming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"香港既話你要自己考慮前境啦<br />\n講數 你又唔夠phy math 專 講programming 又未必夠comp鬥<br />\n唔知phy chem用咩code<br />\nMetlab R 都仲可能入到金融界掛<br />\n一係要考慮下大陸勞動市場<br />\n<br />\n同埋讀mphil 唔讀phd 我都唔知市場會點睇 我既偏見就係普通市場唔會睇sci mphil 都係當空白處理 同番普通ugrad爭<br />\n但上左phd就好難出番普通市場 （除左跑數post/公務員）<br />\n<br />\n如果你好有興趣咪讀個mphil玩下 好似啲人去wh gap一兩年咁<br />\n<br />\n我當年都唔信research exp 係香港係liability <br />\n最後做緊啲唔洗學位既post 兼比19 hr 壓到低過市價<br />\n當然 只係因為我個人本身較廢 都有好多sci grad考到eo<br />\n<br />\n自己衡量下自身能力 skillset 興趣 financial resources 同 理想 啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 轉數慢口材差"},{"pid":"1354b5b40fca9a22698112fa32502d761c15d058","tid":1036904,"uid":180707,"like":0,